## Fossil evidence of overlap

* anatomically modern human (AMH) fossils: Africa 190 kya
* Middle east
    * AMH, 113 kya (warm, wet period)
	* Neanderthals, 60-55 kya
* Asia: AMH 46-34 kya, some Neanderthal ancestry
* Australia: AMH 38-42 kya
* Europe: AMH 34 kya

**Note**: it's complicated and the story will probably change!

